HEADWORD: Omnium
<hw>Om"ni*um</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., of all, gen. pl.
of <ets>omnis</ets> all.]</ety> <fld>(Eng. Stock Exchange)</fld>
<def>The aggregate value of the different stocks in which a loan to
government is now usually funded.</def> <rj><au>M'Culloch.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
